high_descs: turn around and move forward to the sink on the right, turn and face the sink
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the sink
turn to the right and move forward across the kitchen and turn right at the round table, turn right and move forward to the table
put the knife into the white coffee mug that is on the table
pick up the mug with the knife inside of it
turn to the right and move forward back across the kitchen and turn right again to move to back to the sink
put the mug with the knife in to the sink to the right of the white cup that is in the sink
anns.task_desc: put a mug with a knife in to the sink

high_descs: Turn around to the left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around to the right and walk to the table in the corner of the room.
Place the knife into the white mug that is on the table.
Pick up the mug with the knife from the table.
Turn around to the right and walk to the sink.
Place the mug with the knife into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug containing a knife from a table to a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn right and veer right to the circular table.
Place the knife in the mug on the table.
Pick up the mug.
Turn around and veer left, back to the sink.
Place the mug in the sink to the right of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a knife in it in the sink.
